@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #89503 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
I tend to agree, we want to check this before lands in stable

I will demote this to P-high since the crater run showed very little impact and by reading the comments from October it is not a straightforward thing to fix. Also it has landed in stable since then and I _think_ it hasn't had a substancial real-world effect
(pls fix my thinking on that, if needed)
